-- Feinberg to be executive pay czar: White House
-- 
-- Wed Jun 10, 2009 2:51pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/06/10/us-financial-compensation-feinberg-sb-idUSTRE55965E20090610

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - Washington lawyer Kenneth Feinberg will become the Obama administration's "special master" to review executive compensation packages for companies who have received exceptional government assistance, the White House said on Wednesday. 

 (Reporting by  Doug Palmer ; editing by  Doina Chiacu )